MULTER ??
When a user wants to:

    Upload a resume (PDF) 📄

    Upload a profile image 🖼️

We need to:

    Accept it ✅

    Validate it (PDF? Image?) 🔍

    Save it in the right spot 🗂️

And Multer handles all that.
Multer is just one of these helpers (middleware) — but it's special because it:

    Parses multipart/form-data (used for file uploads)

    Saves the uploaded files (to memory or disk)

    Adds req.file or req.files to your request

MULTER VS MIDDELWARE
-> Middleware is a concept — it’s any function that runs between a request and a response.

Multer is a specific middleware that handles file uploads.
